attachments.text:
xLabs is excited to announce that we are joining the Canton Network as a validator, reinforcing our commitment to secure, interoperable, and privacy-preserving blockchain solutions.

The Canton Network introduces a novel paradigm that solves the limitations of existing blockchains, particularly in privacy, scalability, and governance. It enables financial institutions and enterprises to integrate blockchain technology without compromising control, compliance, or operational efficiency.

Learn more on our blog: <https://lnkd.in/ds3hwkpy>

Special thanks to Sophia Roman, Wayne Collier, the Digital Asset team, the Canton Validators community and the Global Synchronizer Foundation (GSF) team, for their support.
